top_comments.comment: Hi Emily I was on the verge of being excited when you pulled out the cooler toned palette with those purples and turquoises, but alas no we got the much more familiar warm toned palette demoed.  Overall as ever I enjoyed the video, but as a pale/cool toned person I would never wear those warm tones and would have liked seeing that other palette chosen - just as something a bit different.  Autumn/Fall tones for me don't include anything orange based and instead I use green/khaki, mauve, plum and burgundy shades.  The cooler toned palette had more of a Winter or party vibe and something a little less seen in affordable brands.  Best wishes.

comments_since_last_sample.body: I’ve been really enjoying the Milani cream blush palette! Glad to see you liked it!
